    "title": "ファンレター",
    "text": [
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "トレーニング前にトレーナー室を訪れると、\nすでにサトノダイヤモンドが到着していた。\n何かを読んでいるようだが――",
            "enText": "When I visited the trainer's office before \ntraining, Satono Diamond had already arrived. \nShe seemed to be reading something―",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "origClipLength": 118,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 129,
                    "pathId": 1041139515768772240
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 129,
                    "pathId": 8460374877995589713
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 4714108050736028079,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "サトノダイヤモンド",
            "enName": "Satono Diamond",
            "jpText": "……文字には、\n書く方の想いがこもるものなのですね。",
            "enText": "…… is the writer's thought that \ngoes into every letter.",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "origClipLength": 78,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "文字？",
                    "enText": "Characters?",
                    "nextBlock": 3
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 89,
                    "pathId": 8628749547193477897
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 89,
                    "pathId": 7168431984254032022
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3964570083764072630,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "サトノダイヤモンド",
            "enName": "Satono Diamond",
            "jpText": "ええ、私宛てにファンレターが\n届いておりまして。",
            "enText": "Yes, I received a fan letter addressed to me.",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "origClipLength": 76,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 147,
                    "pathId": 3334167561078506899
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 87,
                    "pathId": -3769513995508115025
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 87,
                    "pathId": -3638976988728798448
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1658023288071989075,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "サトノダイヤモンド",
            "enName": "Satono Diamond",
            "jpText": "その文字には強い気持ちが滲んでいて……\nつい何度も読み返してしまうのです。",
            "enText": "The letters are so imbued with strong \nfeelings that…… I find myself reading them \nover and over again.",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "origClipLength": 93,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "どんな内容か聞いてもいい？",
                    "enText": "May I ask what it's about?",
                    "nextBlock": 5
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 118,
                    "pathId": 2502490012169027237
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 104,
                    "pathId": -4585617143117965678
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 104,
                    "pathId": 2999475746337922983
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1840826871615547893,
            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "サトノダイヤモンド",
            "enName": "Satono Diamond",
            "jpText": "はい。この方は――",
            "enText": "Yes, sir. This gentleman is―",
            "nextBlock": 6,
            "origClipLength": 56,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -6093924794906675013
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 67,
                    "pathId": 1067799867837591174
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 67,
                    "pathId": -4003793221367767112
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1323131765300337240,
            "blockIdx": 5
        },
        {
            "jpName": "サトノダイヤモンド",
            "enName": "Satono Diamond",
            "jpText": "……立ち上げた事業が失敗し、人生に\n暗雲が立ち込めたことがあったそうです。",
            "enText": "…… a business she started failed, and there \nwas a dark cloud over her life.",
            "nextBlock": 7,
            "origClipLength": 93,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 23,
                    "pathId": -1225344714519086235
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 23,
                    "pathId": -3394896506712162198
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8156184626369654730,
            "blockIdx": 6
        },
        {
            "jpName": "サトノダイヤモンド",
            "enName": "Satono Diamond",
            "jpText": "家族へ申し訳ないという想いも募り、\nどうしていいかわからない日々が続いた、と。",
            "enText": "She felt sorry for her family, and she did \nnot know what to do.",
            "nextBlock": 8,
            "origClipLength": 95,
            "pathId": -4288954871281810433,
            "blockIdx": 7
        },
        {
            "jpName": "サトノダイヤモンド",
            "enName": "Satono Diamond",
            "jpText": "ですがある時、たまたま私の出ていた\nレースをテレビで見たらしく――",
            "enText": "But one day, she happened \nto see me in a race on TV.",
            "nextBlock": 9,
            "origClipLength": 88,
            "pathId": -2195039341995181346,
            "blockIdx": 8
        },
        {
            "jpName": "サトノダイヤモンド",
            "enName": "Satono Diamond",
            "jpText": "『ジンクスを破るため』という私の\n強い意志に勇気をもらったとのことなのです。",
            "enText": "She said she was encouraged by my strong will \nto \"break the jinx.",
            "nextBlock": 10,
            "origClipLength": 94,
            "pathId": 8508109692581057140,
            "blockIdx": 9
        },
        {
            "jpName": "サトノダイヤモンド",
            "enName": "Satono Diamond",
            "jpText": "そして今は別のお仕事をしつつ、\n夢を諦めずに少しずつ次の事業の構想を\n練っているのだとか。",
            "enText": "And now, while working at her other \njob, she is gradually developing a \nplan for her next business venture, \nwithout giving up on her dream.",
            "nextBlock": 11,
            "origClipLength": 103,
            "pathId": -6108720214982838918,
            "blockIdx": 10
        },
        {
            "jpName": "サトノダイヤモンド",
            "enName": "Satono Diamond",
            "jpText": "……字は時折震え、時折強くなっていますが、\r\n最後にはしっかりと名が記されています。",
            "enText": "The…… letters are sometimes shaky, \nsometimes strong, but the name is \nfirmly marked at the end.",
            "nextBlock": 12,
            "origClipLength": 99,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 181,
                    "pathId": 4433005003019649133
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 192,
                    "pathId": -4417741370607558537
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6693503045301088226,
            "blockIdx": 11
        },
        {
            "jpName": "サトノダイヤモンド",
            "enName": "Satono Diamond",
            "jpText": "きっとこの方も覚悟を決め、私と同じように\n道を切り拓こうと努力していらっしゃる\nのでしょう。",
            "enText": "I am sure that this person has \nmade up her mind and is striving \nto pave the way just as I am.",
            "nextBlock": 13,
            "origClipLength": 105,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 260,
                    "pathId": -561883712524545112
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 116,
                    "pathId": 7012964797278615988
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 116,
                    "pathId": 7018037359355796079
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -484525491738714420,
            "blockIdx": 12
        },
        {
            "jpName": "サトノダイヤモンド",
            "enName": "Satono Diamond",
            "jpText": "つまり――同志というわけです。",
            "enText": "So - we are coMs.des.",
            "nextBlock": 14,
            "origClipLength": 64,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -7461261933095095063
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 52,
                    "pathId": 1017638096199760333
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 168,
                    "pathId": -2541548424851974662
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -5449403770432161350,
            "blockIdx": 13
        },
        {
            "jpName": "サトノダイヤモンド",
            "enName": "Satono Diamond",
            "jpText": "ふふっ、同志が頑張っているのであれば、\n私ももたもたしてはいられませんね。",
            "enText": "Well, if my coMs.des are doing their best, I \ncan't afford to be slow.",
            "nextBlock": 15,
            "origClipLength": 93,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 74,
                    "pathId": -5652121277146618556
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 104,
                    "pathId": -6235759459533885403
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8141635974673978855,
            "blockIdx": 14
        },
        {
            "jpName": "サトノダイヤモンド",
            "enName": "Satono Diamond",
            "jpText": "さあ、今日もトレーニングに励むと\nいたしましょう。新たな道を切り拓くために！",
            "enText": "Let's get training again today! \nTo open up new avenues!",
            "nextBlock": -1,
            "origClipLength": 94,
